response.overview: Alice is young and sassy gal Mama who manages a small army of 10 sons.  The mornings are really chaotic in this house, but she does her best effort to take care of “everything”.  This story has a lil’ trouble as Alice (the actress) is only 29 years old and clearly too young to be casted in this role. But let’s be honest, we can safely not give a damn, since this is the best Alice Otsu video since probably forever.  First addition to this series in 3 years. This low hurdles video is pure gold.
